v1.0.7.22	05-May-2021 - Andrew Leary

		1.  Added a switch to mbsetup for force tossing of NetMail
                packets only from the unprotected inbound.  The default is off.
		ARCmail packets in the unprotected inbound will still only be
		tossed if mbfido is called with the -unp switch.

		2.  Updated copyright notices to 2021.

v1.0.7.23	31-Oct-2021 - Andrew Leary

		1.  Door dropfiles will now list the actual or locked port
		speed, instead of being forced to 19200 bps.

		2.  Corrected the FidoNet address for FREQing the current
		release of MBSEBBS.

		3.  A few other minor spelling/grammer corrections.
